{"tid":1957233,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"長期胃氣脹真係好辛苦好想死","createTime":"2020-04-03T17:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T05:10:34.000Z","uid":175902,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"1b00b16f03bee41053e53d5de07e595c2357b6f2","tid":1957233,"uid":175902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:53:50.000Z","msg":"未到25歲 個胃長期都脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔食野都勁多氣 飲水同食少少野都脹到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而無試過胃痛 又少打司嗝 淨係成日都有胃氣 主動嗝極都仲有 永遠都唔會停 道氣就係咁頂住喉嚨 呢排嚴重佐頂到有啲呼吸困難以為中撚佐武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過無數個方法 中西醫都睇過無好番過 胃仙U、軟殻散乜胃藥都試過都無用 黎緊諗住去照胃鏡<br />\n偏方試過 以為胃酸過少 飲蘋果醋 檸檬水 <br />\n以為胃下垂練腹肌 全部都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪已經無得救以後都要同胃氣共存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人同我一樣 可唔可以救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14142604372a3c6b706bbad71cff079c0204b58","tid":1957233,"uid":48769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:55:55.000Z","msg":"縮肚吐氣OK?<br />\n吐晒就會細返"},{"pid":"ec5157bf559d041baf5d3bc7365fbae881637ecf","tid":1957233,"uid":175902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c14142604372a3c6b706bbad71cff079c0204b58","tid":1957233,"uid":48769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:55:55.000Z","msg":"縮肚吐氣OK?<br />\n吐晒就會細返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:57:53.000Z","msg":"成日都會咁做 嗝勁都有 <br />\n就好似鼻敏感呻鼻涕咁 根本無幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d3abb2f19e0efc490c66fb011e860310e8a512","tid":1957233,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:58:22.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"7c73de6c71b55c1d34c82d3414cb