但一出太陽 天氣一乾爽就會好好多"},{"pid":"e1ad70c60d36dd13eeec8b00991cb207531a5a4e","tid":1957233,"uid":46072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"有無人有專科醫生介紹<br />\n想見醫生同照大腸鏡<br />\n肚右下夜晚成日會脹痛<br />\n好似有舊野係入面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36912d8b0a2fa2564049a7dcfa4fe71de9800a6d","tid":1957233,"uid":45844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"認真, 試吓飲可樂"}]}